"{\"uid\": \"thesouthafrican.com-sport-paris-olympics-2024-tatjana-paris-olympics-i-swam-for-everyone-been-there-for-me\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Copyright Blue Sky Publications (Pty) Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 63, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 15, \"end\": 18, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.7675180524712429, \"rank\": 0.30041794323702614, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"thesouthafrican.com is a division of Blue Sky Publications Ltd. Reproduction without permission prohibited  Home\\u00bbSport\\u00bbParis Olympics 2024\\u00bbTatjana Smith in Paris: \\\"I had no idea where I was, literally most of the race\\\"  What a moment.\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 107, \"end\": 110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"score\": 0.7675180524712429, \"rank\": 0.30041794323702614, \"text\": \"Sky\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_UK\"}, {\"begin\": 221, \"end\": 226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997153282, \"rank\": 2.84752217646287e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tatjana Smith could not hide her sheer delight after claiming gold in the 100m breaststroke event at the Paris 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 301, \"to\": 426, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had no idea where I was, literally most of the race,\\\" admitted Smith afterwards.\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I actually did not think I medalled because when I turned to my left, the two blocks next to me both had lights on and it felt like someone else on the other side touched first.\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 691, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I actually did not think I was medalling.\", \"from\": 693, \"to\": 738, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My main goal was just to not do what I did in Tokyo and look around, so literally the last 15 metres, I was like, no, close your eyes, let us just go.\\\"\", \"from\": 740, \"to\": 892, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 787, \"end\": 792, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8803242311137665, \"rank\": 0.13593941311838878, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I swam for everyone that's been there for me, that's believed with me, for our country as well.\\\"\", \"from\": 894, \"to\": 991, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tatjana Smith was the resounding pre-race favourite for the 100m breaststroke event after winning her heat and semi-finals.\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She broke the world record to claim 200m gold in Tokyo three years ago and now she's climbed to the top of the mountain in the shorter race.\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1257, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1166, \"end\": 1171, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8803242311137665, \"rank\": 0.13593941311838878, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She touched the wall first in1.05.28despite a less-than-perfect first lap and thanks to a stunning surge in the final 25.\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1379, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"China's Tang Qianting scooped silver and a visibly delighted Mona McSharry, from Ireland, got the bronze.\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1485, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1380, \"end\": 1385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999829433390388, \"rank\": 1.6721884772992438e-05, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1388, \"end\": 1401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tang_Qianting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tang Qianting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tang_Qianting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tang_Qianting\"}, {\"begin\": 1441, \"end\": 1454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mona McSharry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_McSharry\"}, {\"begin\": 1461, \"end\": 1468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.6677940137065915, \"rank\": 0.49745664927335903, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith stands to become only the second swimmer in history after Penny Heyns in 1996 to complete the 100m and 200m breaststroke golden double at the same Olympics event.\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1655, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1551, \"end\": 1562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penelope_Heyns\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Penny Heyns\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penelope_Heyns\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penelope_Heyns\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith wasn't yet born when Heyns accomplished this historic feat.\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1721, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old contests her 200m breaststroke heat onWednesday 31 July at 11:00 SA timewith thesemi-finals going at 21:51 and 21:58.The finalis onThursday 01 August at 21:04.You know thatNando's will be watching.\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1935, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Smith won this event in Tokyo with a time of 2.18.95, a world record at the time.\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 2017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1960, \"end\": 1965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8803242311137665, \"rank\": 0.13593941311838878, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You have seen it hundreds of times already but what's the harm in watching it a few more times?\", \"from\": 2019, \"to\": 2114, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the great comebacks in Olympic swimming history.\", \"from\": 2115, \"to\": 2170, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Let us know by clicking on the comment tab below this article or emailinginfo@thesouthafrican.com.\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can also send a WhatsApp to 060 011 021 1.\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2317, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2291, \"end\": 2299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"score\": 0.9972957342505762, \"rank\": 0.002711598632655821, \"text\": \"WhatsApp\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WhatsApp\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow@TheSAnews on XandThe South African on Facebookfo